author: Amanda Jackson, CNN
title: Man released from jail amid coronavirus concerns is arrested on a murder charge
description: Amid rising concerns of the coronavirus being spread in a Florida jail, many inmates were released early, including Joseph Williams. But a day after his release, Williams was arrested on a murder charge.
content:
(CNN)Amid rising concerns of the coronavirus being spread in a Florida jail, many inmates were released early, including Joseph Williams.
